# Catch - 11894-IOV - 8222-ROX

This is a compatibility patch for:

- [Mineral Overhaul (11894-IOV)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11894) by [AsteroidLeaf](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/AsteroidLeaf)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241216012926/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11894)
- [Royal Galaxy - A Starfield Revamp And Cut Content Restoration (8222-ROX)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/8222) by [JaeDL](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/JaeDL)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Profile Page](https://web.archive.org/web/20241215224548/https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/JaeDL)
		- Private messages (Discord)
	- Donate:

		[![Ko-fi Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Ko--fi-white?style=flat&logo=kofi&logoColor=black)](https://ko-fi.com/jaedl)
		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=Upsend@gmail.com)

Both make changes to the same minerals. This compatibility patch merges these so you get the best of both worlds.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This compatibility patch is an independent creation and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially supported by the original author(s) of the mods involved.

Find more compatibility patches here: [Catch Collection](https://github.com/catch-group/catch-collection)

## Recommended Load Order

1. Mineral Overhaul
2. Royal Galaxy - A Starfield Revamp And Cut Content Restoration
3. Catch - 11894-IOV - 8222-ROX
